Class BluetoothProtocol

  • java.lang.Object
    • comm.BluetoothProtocol

  • public final class BluetoothProtocol
extends java.lang.Object
    The protocol to use for communicating data via bluetooth between robot and computer. Each constant represents a byte to send to notify the receiver of the following message.
